news.title: YEIDA orders forensic audit of Ajnara Panorama, to hire private firm
news.para: Through the audit, officials said, the Authority will get an assessment of the construction completed till now, apart from finding out the exact number of flats sold and possession given to buyers to date.

news.title: Ahmedabad: Shilp Group acquires 21,000 sq yard plot for Rs 200 crore in Gota
news.para: Market sources peg the deal size to be at Rs 200 crore. A luxury residential building is expected to come up on the plot bought by Shilp Group.

news.title: Gurugram: Soon, registry of floors on plots below 180 sq yd?
news.para: Due to restrictions by the state government on registering independent floors built on plots less than 180 sq yd in size in private developer areas, the owners can neither formally own them nor sell the property.
